abstract: Paul Lawrie leads third round of Qatar Masters at the Doha Golf Club; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Paul Lawrie earned a two-shot lead at the Doha Golf Club to close in on a third Qatar Masters title. Lawrie, the overnight leader, started the third round with 13 pars before making his first birdie on the 14th hole.
